WORKDIR /app

RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
        build-essential \
        libpq-dev \
        unixodbc-dev \
    && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/* \
    && pip install --no-cache-dir poetry==1.8.2

RUN poetry config virtualenvs.in-project true

COPY pyproject.toml poetry.lock ./
RUN poetry install --only main --no-root


FROM python:3.12-slim

LABEL maintainer="infrastructure@example.com" \
      description="Python analytics platform (Superset/Redash inspired)"

WORKDIR /app

RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
        curl \
        libpq-dev \
        unixodbc-dev \
    && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

RUN groupadd -g 1000 superset \
    && useradd -u 1000 -g superset -s /bin/bash -m superset

COPY --chown=superset:superset --from=backend-builder /app/.venv /app/.venv
COPY --chown=superset:superset --from=frontend-builder /app/frontend/dist /app/static
COPY --chown=superset:superset . /app

ENV PATH="/app/.venv/bin:$PATH"

EXPOSE 8088

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:8088/health || exit 1

USER superset

CMD ["gunicorn", "-w", "4", "-b", "0.0.0.0:8088", "app:create_app()"]
